      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u serious? i dont see the fairy dust lol. but like, is it really okay to take two at once? i read somewhere that taking too much triptans can be dangerous. also the face thing is kinda weird, it's like the corner of my mouth is drooping a bit. you're sure it's just a migraine and not something else? i'm kinda scared to go to the er if it's just a migraine",
